# Pixel Art

## Cyberpunk Cityscape

**What:** A 64x64 pixel art depiction of a futuristic cyberpunk cityscape at night, featuring neon-lit skyscrapers, holographic billboards, and a glowing moon reflected on wet streets.

**Why:** I chose this theme because cyberpunk aesthetics naturally lend themselves to vibrant, constrained color palettes that work beautifully in pixel art. The contrast between dark shadows and bright neon creates visual depth and evokes a sense of wonder about technological futures.